{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Exit ECHR & do not pay families of failed asylum seekers up to \u00a340k to leave UK",
        "additional_details": "We feel that it is not acceptable to give money away like this. In our view, it is not an incentive and is a waste of more money. We also call on the Government to leave the ECHR, and remove people with failed asylum claims.",
        "background": "Stop the pilot scheme to pay families of failed asylum seekers up to \u00a340K to leave the UK. In our view, Government cannot be allowed to pay people who have not gotten asylum with our taxpayer money. There is a cost of living crisis, and we think we need money for defence. We should also exit ECHR. ",
